            <div class="p-6 border-b">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Recent Discussions</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="divide-y">
                <div class="p-6 hover:bg-gray-50 cursor-pointer">
                    <div class="flex items-start justify-between">
                        <div class="flex-1">
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Best practices for chama investments in 2025</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">What investment strategies have worked well for your chama this year? Looking for ideas for property, stocks, and business ventures.</p>
                            <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-500">
                                <span class="mr-4">Posted by <span class="font-medium">Sarah Wanjiku</span></span>
                                <span class="mr-4">2 hours ago</span>
                                <span>23 replies</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="ml-4">
                            <span class="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-green-100 text-green-800">
                                Investment
                            </span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="p-6 hover:bg-gray-50 cursor-pointer">
                    <div class="flex items-start justify-between">
                        <div class="flex-1">
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Managing member contributions during economic uncertainty</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">How has your chama adapted to the current economic climate? Any strategies for maintaining steady contributions?</p>
                            <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-500">
                                <span class="mr-4">Posted by <span class="font-medium">David Kiprop</span></span>
                                <span class="mr-4">5 hours ago</span>
                                <span>18 replies</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="ml-4">
                            <span class="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-blue-100 text-blue-800">
                                Management
                            </span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="p-6 hover:bg-gray-50 cursor-pointer">
                    <div class="flex items-start justify-between">
                        <div class="flex-1">
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Digital tools for chama accounting - recommendations?</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">What digital tools are you using for chama accounting and financial management? Pros and cons of different platforms.</p>
                            <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-500">
                                <span class="mr-4">Posted by <span class="font-medium">Grace Achieng</span></span>
                                <span class="mr-4">1 day ago</span>
                                <span>31 replies</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="ml-4">
                            <span class="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-purple-100 text-purple-800">
                                Technology
                            </span>
                        </div>
