            <p class="text-xl mb-8 opacity-90">Connect with thousands of chama members, share your experiences, and grow your financial knowledge.</p>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
                <a href="register" class="bg-white text-green-600 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors font-semibold text-lg">
